    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR6q0610-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s015" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">Where does the monk speak for someone?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s016" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">Huang said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s017" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"If you don't understand clearly,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s018" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">then I will put my palms together."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s019" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"When I sit,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s020" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">you stand in attendance."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s021" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"If you bring tea,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s022" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">I will receive it for you."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s023" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">The master was silent for a long time.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s024" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">Huang said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s025" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"Seeing is seeing;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s026" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">to contemplate is to err."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0106-s027" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">The master then had a great awakening.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-h001" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">107</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s002" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">Great Master Yunmen said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s003" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"If the light does not penetrate completely,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s004" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">there are two kinds of illnesses.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s005" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">Not being clear in all places,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s006" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">and having something in front of you, is one."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s007" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"Even if you penetrate the emptiness of all dharmas,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s008" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">and there seems to be something faintly similar,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s009" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">that is also a case of the light not penetrating completely."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s010" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"Furthermore, the Dharmakaya also has two kinds of illnesses.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s011" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">Attaining the Dharmakaya,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s012" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">and not forgetting attachment to the Dharma,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s013" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">and still having one's own views,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s014" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">is one: falling on the side of the Dharmakaya."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s015" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"Even if you penetrate it thoroughly,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s016" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">it is impermissible to let it go."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s017" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">"If you carefully examine it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0107-s018" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">having any trace of breath is also an illness."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0108-h001" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">108</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0108-s002" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">Mazu,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0108-s003" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-23T10:26:06.913+09:00">because a monk asked,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0090-s120" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Having spoken, he kicked over the boat,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0090-s121" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">and disappeared into the mist and waves.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-h001" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">91</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s002" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Huangbo, addressing the assembly, said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s003" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"All the old masters of other places</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s004" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">are all on the top of my staff."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s005" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">A monk bowed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s006" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Later, arriving at the place of Great Tree,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s007" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">he raised the previous story.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s008" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Great Tree said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s009" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"Huangbo said that,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s010" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">has he ever actually seen the other places or not?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s011" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">The monk returned and spoke of Huangbo.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s012" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Huangbo said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s013" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"My words have already spread throughout the world."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s014" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Langye Jue said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s015" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"Great Tree's saying that</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s016" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">is too much like having eyes but being blind."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s017" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Huangbo's one staff,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0091-s018" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">the people of the world chew on it but cannot break it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-h001" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">92</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s002" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Chan Master Huiran of Three Saints Monastery,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s003" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">a successor of Linji,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s004" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s005" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"When I meet someone, I release it immediately;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s006" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">releasing it is not for the sake of others."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s007" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Xinghua said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s008" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"When I meet someone, I don't release it immediately;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0092-s009" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">releasing it is precisely for the sake of others."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0093-h001" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">93</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0093-s002" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Chan Master Mi was holding a needle,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0093-s003" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">Dongshan asked,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0093-s004" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"What are you doing?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0093-s005" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">The Master said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0610_DZZ_0093-s006" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T16:45:46.941+09:00">"Holding a needle."</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
